{"tid":760913,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[以暴亦暴治人渣] 囚犯是理應被虐待的！","createTime":"2018-07-30T03:17:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-30T06:06:53.000Z","uid":49388,"like":4,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bfc8f05d9e41b922a20f3344cfc2aa5dfd1c1762","tid":760913,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T03:17:13.000Z","msg":"犯得事理撚得你大事定小事，總之坐得監入得賊就必定壞人！呢個根本係無得爭議。<br />\n<br />\n由其係少年階段，學壞左仲有得救！而入得少年勞教就要用非一般手段去重新教導！<br />\n<br />\n大量體罰，逼令食屎飲尿食滾粥，踼春袋，罰當眾打飛機再自己吞精等等好多都聽聞過，好似好不人道，但你要記住入得黎只係一個囚犯，難聽D講句佢地只係一件社會垃圾！虐待到佢驚知死，佢地從良就當教好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 死撚埋就當修理下D人渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔犯事就唔會有今日，出得黎行預左要還<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前係出面大支野入到好俾柳記撚到屎都不如諗起都開心<br />\n唔好同我講囚權，囚犯根本連人權都唔可以有！呢D説話只係俾一班左權用來顯得自己特別清高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以暴亦暴就係解決問題既方法，以德報怨愛與和平只係用黎呃傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 美帝夠大把虐囚例子，D犯全部被虐至半身不遂，被羞辱到無哂自尊連屎都不如，但當你諗到呢係恐佈分子時就會有一點心涼。<br />\n<br />\n請記住，世界上有D人係需要被虐待的！<br />\n<br />\n（以上觀點只適用於民主國家）"},{"pid":"5f3882289d6f2537d0b37ecb2104226399904b85","tid":760913,"uid":192491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T03:25:26.000Z","msg":"要以德報怨呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de6fadb6e677dc336d4047b9312163896a41efde","tid":760913,"uid":197157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f3882289d6f2537d0b37ecb2104226399904b85","tid":760913,"uid":192491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T03:25:26.000Z","msg":"要以德報怨呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T03:28:29.000Z","msg":"何以報德<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fcc0b9d19242378639acbc7a0f67215dc66390b","tid":760913,"uid":154218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de6fadb6e677dc336d4047b9312163896a41efde","tid":760913,"uid":197157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f3882289d6f2537d0b37ecb2104226399904b85","tid":760913,"uid":192491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T03:25:26.000Z","msg":"要以德報怨呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T03:28:29.000Z","msg":"何以報德<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T03:36:54.000Z","msg":"以怨"},{"pid":"194c048de1353f0dd74cbf1564d9f19d944e7577","tid":760913,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T03:57:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4ac173541c9596ed12579a4b515c576dc4c3102","tid":760913,"uid":35440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T03:59:18.000Z","msg":"以德報怨 何以報德<br />\n以直報怨 以德報德<br />\n<br />\n但又咁 你唔當佢係人咁處置 佢又點會似返個人？"},{"pid":"fbf4bc7bc727de2f1245839b2d9a362270bbf024","tid":760913,"uid":82829,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T04:26:14.000Z","msg":"做乜鳩<br />\n咁不如直接啪哂佢<br />\n又唔洗哂錢<br />\n又慳位"},{"pid":"84a69b6ce4818a118cdd4f8d874395687cee773e","tid":760913,"uid":44391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T05:57:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d6ab8f30f5ad156725aa6fa4c0453d58933ec627","tid":760913,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T05:58:06.000Z","msg":"坑殺左佢地咪算"},{"pid":"8d92fc716bc3c8463210ee1570f4b0873fa3a5bd","tid":760913,"uid":61485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T06:06:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images.gr-assets.com/hostedimages/1445804342ra/16704388.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gr-assets.com%2Fhostedimages%2F1445804342ra%2F16704388.gif&h=79cbb88f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"htt